There are 3 synonyms for the same function PlotVector () PlotVector2D () arrow ()
PlotVector (Vect); - std basis, tail at origin, default color PlotVector (Vect, 'style'); - std basis, tail at origin PlotVector (tail, Vect, 'style'); - std basis PlotVector (Vect, basis, 'style'); - tail at origin PlotVector (tail, Vect, basis, 'style');
'tail' and 'Vect' are columns, 2 elements 'basis' is matrix, 2x2 'style' optional, must be last arg if present
